Description: Multiverse analyses run the same analysis over a
    range of arbitrary data processing decisions. 'multitool' provides an 
    interface for creating alternative analysis pipelines and turning then into a 
    grid of all possible pipelines. Using this grid as a blueprint, you can 
    model your data with all possible analysis pipelines and summarize the results.
